sections.heading: of State; record; public examination
sections.text: The Secretary of State shall keep for public examination a record of all trade names registered or renewed under sections 87-208 to 87-219.01.SourceLaws 1967, c. 628, ยง 6, p. 2102;Laws 1997, LB 453, ยง 11;Laws 2011, LB462, ยง 13.
